Java program to display Diamond Patteern:

Firstly, I have created a public class named DiamondPattern.
I have defined main method to begin the execution.
I have created Scanner class to take input from the user.
I have initialized a variable n with zero.
I am asking user to enter the N value.
I have created a printStarDiamond method and passing parameter n.
I am displaying to enter the positive number.
I am increasing the portion.
I am printing the space.
I am printing the Star.
I am decreasing the portion.
Finally, I am displaying the Diamond pattern.

TestCase:

There are different diamond patterns are availble in Java.Now, let us start with 
a full diamond pattern.

Input-1 :

Enter N value ::
 6
 
